Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:CP:wifi: ath12k: Add missing htt stats

Add missing FW stats as part of HTT stats type 1, 10, 17, 27, 30, 37,
38, 42, 48 and 57.

Patch-dependency: ath12k/0280-0001-wifi-ath12k-Add-debugfs-support.patch
Patch-work: None

Signed-off-by: Rajat Soni <rajson@qti.qualcomm.com>
